Maintaining fonts.

Stich.php will create sprites of each font category.  It will also create fonts.json.

1) run "http://des.pictographr.com/php/admin/stich.php" in order to get an updated
fonts.json file in dir: /uploads/output.

2) http://des.pictographr.com/php/admin/fonts_naming.html will pull fonts.json.

3) fonts_naming.html will update fonts_naming.json in dir: /uploads/output whenever
input fields Label or Family are keyUp. This is done in admin controller.

4) Refresh stich.php so it can pull the latest fonts_naming.json and generate a newer fonts.json.

5) remember to sudo chown -R apache:apache /var/www/pictographr-design/uploads if you move any
file from local computer to uploads directory.
